data.description:
Kick your feet up in front of the wood burning fireplace, enjoy the spacious kitchen, or spend time in the sizable back yard of this beautiful home! Being less than quarter of a mile from downtown Fennville, this house offers you the comfortability without sacrificing convenience.
 
This home has big bathrooms, natural light, plenty of storage space, and a lot of potential! This house is perfect for the person who wants a move in ready house with the potential to make it your own. The large garage also offers you all the room you could need for multiple vehicles, hobbies, or storage. Come see why this one won't last long, and schedule a private showing today!
